# GitHub Linguist language-bar fix.
#
# Linguist excludes "prose" languages (Markdown, plain text) from the
# repository language statistics by default. Since this repo is almost
# entirely Markdown documentation, that left the language bar showing
# "Makefile 100%" — the lone Makefile being the only file Linguist
# counts as a programming language.
#
# Forcing Markdown to be detectable makes the language bar reflect what
# the repository actually is: overwhelmingly Markdown, with a small
# Makefile slice.
*.md linguist-detectable=true
